{"tid":1508480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷疑Fake News] 關於懷疑有女示威者被__","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T22:13:27.000Z","uid":267172,"like":191,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"4aed5379915f185371cbe2ee9b57ac1a8c4b66aa","tid":1508480,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"標題唔寫輪姦因為我唔想幫仆街五毛製造恐慌<br />\n<br />\n（未FC) 聲稱有女示威者被強姦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508384</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個post段字我睇住一個user 係TG 公海出<br />\n第一次出嘅時候佢大大聲話自己手足一手料比佢<br />\n但有人追問FC同邊間醫院<br />\n佢就無再出聲<br />\n我唔知佢係潛水定fact check緊<br />\n<br />\n我睇左一陣就無再追post，如果有update請你地話我知<br />\n<br />\n但我唔想你地再post果張圖出黎製造恐慌<br />\n要追查 唔需要用咁煽情嘅字眼<br />\n<br />\nFake news 會令你地習慣恐怖嘅新聞<br />\n令你覺得黑警做嘅野「好似無咁過份」<br />\n同時製造白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n請你地想factcheck嘅時候刪去煽情字眼"},{"pid":"e9332f3d8a7b3a15765eed06e7a61d1db9910f35","tid":1508480,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8f915ed34423e3b5fd04ec2b0f9e54fd7897adf","tid":1508480,"uid":267172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到post<br />\n靠你地。"},{"pid":"5f65efe2e11af6d54dbba6462d0e47948825071b","tid":1508480,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca5c43245399fc26ecbe79c3f066caa2888c5cf2","tid":1508480,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0242d15f267337d88dc73d0ac7728a0bb9aa01d","tid":1508480,"uid":114032,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"re